thrives on differences,

00:03:40.370 --> 00:03:45.440 align:middle line:84%
and it's inherently
creative, and yet

00:03:45.440 --> 00:03:49.580 align:middle line:90%
cooperative and interdependent.

00:03:49.580 --> 00:03:56.870 align:middle line:84%
And it allows for growth,
and allows for freedom.

00:03:56.870 --> 00:04:00.090 align:middle line:90%


00:04:00.090 --> 00:04:02.840 align:middle line:90%
That's what I see as abundance.

