out energy constantly.

00:04:51.630 --> 00:04:53.400 align:middle line:90%
Look at the world.

00:04:53.400 --> 00:04:59.430 align:middle line:84%
Plants growing, the sea
moving, the planets orbiting.

00:04:59.430 --> 00:05:02.360 align:middle line:90%
Galaxies spinning.

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:03.210 align:middle line:90%
You know?

00:05:03.210 --> 00:05:09.690 align:middle line:84%
We're constantly in growth and
motion and perpetual abundance.

00:05:09.690 --> 00:05:12.180 align:middle line:84%
So we can have it just
because it exists.

00:05:12.180 --> 00:05:13.853 align:middle line:90%
And we're part of this creation.

