00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:44.340 align:middle line:90%
Who would you love to touch?

00:05:44.340 --> 00:05:46.480 align:middle line:90%
Who would you love to serve?

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:48.150 align:middle line:84%
What would you
like to experience?

00:05:48.150 --> 00:05:49.070 align:middle line:90%
Taste?

00:05:49.070 --> 00:05:49.950 align:middle line:90%
Eat?

00:05:49.950 --> 00:05:52.110 align:middle line:90%
What would you like to wear?

00:05:52.110 --> 00:05:54.750 align:middle line:90%
How would you like to travel?

00:05:54.750 --> 00:05:58.830 align:middle line:84%
Where would you
like to travel to?

00:05:58.830 --> 00:06:03.740 align:middle line:84%
What people is your
soul yearning to meet?

00:06:03.740 --> 00:06:09.660 align:middle line:84%
What places in the world are
you feeling drawn and called to?

00:06:09.660 --> 00:06:12.300 align:middle line:84%
>> There are two things that
drive us past our current

00:06:12.300 --> 00:06:13.740 align:middle line:90%
