00:06:13.740 --> 00:06:16.080 align:middle line:90%
Hope and dreams.

00:06:16.080 --> 00:06:19.770 align:middle line:84%
And it's the belief
that there is more.

00:06:19.770 --> 00:06:22.500 align:middle line:84%
The belief that this
isn't all there is.

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:28.560 align:middle line:84%
The belief that I can exceed
my current limitations.

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:33.660 align:middle line:84%
And without that vision, without
that dream, without that hope,

00:06:33.660 --> 00:06:34.770 align:middle line:90%
we stay stuck.

00:06:34.770 --> 00:06:38.170 align:middle line:84%
We stay where we are because
anything else is too fearful.

00:06:38.170 --> 00:06:40.800 align:middle line:84%
It's that that lets us
step past that threshold

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:45.060 align:middle line:84%
