experience something.

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:46.530 align:middle line:90%
Face the fear.

00:06:46.530 --> 00:06:48.720 align:middle line:90%
Move through the fear.

00:06:48.720 --> 00:06:51.300 align:middle line:84%
