to be a little bit scary,

00:06:51.300 --> 00:06:54.110 align:middle line:84%
but there is a
dream beyond that.

00:06:54.110 --> 00:06:56.800 align:middle line:84%
And so it's looking
at the dream.

00:06:56.800 --> 00:06:58.410 align:middle line:90%
It's focusing on the dream.

00:06:58.410 --> 00:07:04.740 align:middle line:84%
It's attaching your life,
your actions, your thinking,

00:07:04.740 --> 00:07:07.230 align:middle line:84%
to the hope as
opposed to the fear

00:07:07.230 --> 00:07:09.900 align:middle line:84%
that lets us step past
that space and experience

00:07:09.900 --> 00:07:11.090 align:middle line:90%
something else.

00:07:11.090 --> 00:07:13.590 align:middle line:84%
>> And if you think about action
from the point of view that

00:07:13.590 --> 00:07:16.140 align:middle line:84%
