00:07:33.450 --> 00:07:35.033 align:middle line:84%
But there's a problem
with that model.

00:07:35.033 --> 00:07:37.350 align:middle line:84%
And the problem is, no
matter how many butterflies

00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:39.660 align:middle line:84%
