day when you wake up,

00:07:39.660 --> 00:07:41.280 align:middle line:90%
you've got to chase again.

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:43.350 align:middle line:84%
And if you stop chasing,
all those butterflies,

00:07:43.350 --> 00:07:45.240 align:middle line:90%
they disappear.

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:46.688 align:middle line:84%
Whereas you'll
