garden, well, you're

00:07:52.965 --> 00:07:54.465 align:middle line:84%
not trying to chase
the butterflies.

00:07:54.465 --> 00:07:57.570 align:middle line:84%
But you make it
beautiful with flowers.

00:07:57.570 --> 00:07:58.890 align:middle line:90%
You've got amazing plants.

00:07:58.890 --> 00:08:00.300 align:middle line:84%
You've got an
amazing place which

00:08:00.300 --> 00:08:03.900 align:middle line:84%
actually attracts the birds and
the bees and the butterflies.

00:08:03.900 --> 00:08:05.880 align:middle line:84%
Then, every day, the
butterflies come to you

00:08:05.880 --> 00:08:07.422 align:middle line:84%
