of relationships.

00:08:40.870 --> 00:08:46.430 align:middle line:84%
The wealth of experience
that you have.

00:08:46.430 --> 00:08:49.050 align:middle line:84%
For me, it was
having my thinking

00:08:49.050 --> 00:08:51.940 align:middle line:84%
