00:09:33.690 --> 00:09:35.130 align:middle line:90%
we're gonna land.

00:09:35.130 --> 00:09:36.260 align:middle line:90%
He's got it made.

00:09:36.260 --> 00:09:38.700 align:middle line:84%
So he talks to me
about the script,

00:09:38.700 --> 00:09:40.080 align:middle line:90%
